Package: kue
Version: 0.1.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Kuetix Team <support@kuetix.com>

Description: CLI tool for Kuetix Engine workflow management
 Kue is a command-line interface for the Kuetix Engine that provides
 workflow management capabilities including:
  - Initialize new workflow projects (kue init)
  - Run workflows locally (kue run)
  - Validate S/WSL/JSON workflow files (kue validate)
  - Run workflow tests (kue test)
Homepage: https://github.com/kuetix/engine
